content.text:
So now that you understand what a circuit and the main components are, you are going to be building your own circuit by following the instructions below:

1. Drag and Drop the Brown Wires onto the Purple tags on the circuit
2. Click on a resistor of your choice (you will be able to change it)
3. Click and hold on the switch to close the circuit, to open circuit, let go of your click
4. Test and try out the different resistors by clicking on them
